<br>
Chardok - 45+<br>
<br>
Lady Vox, Lord Nagafen - Typically 46 - 52 (53+ gets gated out) <br>
<br>
City of Mist - 45+<br>
<br>
Kael Arena - Depending on target, 40+. If Vindi, statue, AoW - expect higher<br>
<br>
Trakanon in Old Sebilis - 55+ <br>
<br>
Plane of Hate - 47+ (Can go at 46, but if you die and delevel, things kinda suck)<br>
<br>
