<br>
Some raids will take any cleric that is 39+.  (Complete Heal is very mana-efficient when cast on a 61 character)<br>
<br>
Chardok:  Min 50+.  Some places take 45+ but I feel they're a liability.<br>
Vox / Nagafen:  Min 46, Max 52 (53+ are on the buff squad)<br>
City of Mist (Torsis):  Min 45, rec 50+.<br>
Kael:  Min 46+.  40's might be able to help on platehouse.<br>
Trakanon:  55+.<br>
Hate:  46.5+ (You need to be able to eat a few deaths.  You will NOT be on a break team.)<br>
Fear:  47+.<br>
