<br>
Chardok - 45+ for the royals, 40+ for everything else<br>
<br>
Lady Vox, Lord Nagafen - 46 - 52 is right, if you go any sooner the AE will kill you fast.<br>
<br>
City of Mist - 35+   Its a GREAT xp zone for the low 40s so how can they not raid the place? Hell, the reavers are only low 50s.<br>
<br>
Kael Arena - 40+ sound about right, most of the giants in the arena are low to mid 50s... just take that into account.<br>
<br>
Trakanon in Old Sebilis - 55 and you will still get eaten by the AE<br>
<br>
Plane of Hate - 46+ is ok<br>
<br>
--Birt<br>
